Title: Alpha
Plot: A mysterious dog thought to be the last of a rare Asian breed is responsible for several murders which Mulder and Scully are investigating. Now the agents have to find a way to stop the dog before it kills again.
GuestStars: Melinda Culea, Thomas Duffy, Michael Mantell, David Starwalt, Andrew Robinson, James Michael Connor, Yau-Gene Chan, Tuan Tuan, Dana Lee, Lisa Picotte, Mady Levin, Treva Tegtmeier, Adrienne Wilde
